{"title":"Hadoop伪分布式安装","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:18.982Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Hadoop伪分布式安装","updated":"2023-07-28T08:55:53.432Z","content":"<h2 id=\"hadoop伪分布式安装\">Hadoop伪分布式安装<a title=\"#hadoop伪分布式安装\" href=\"#hadoop伪分布式安装\"></a></h2>\n<p>首先需要<strong>安装Hadoop环境</strong>，可以参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/115407308\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a></p>\n<p><strong>配置ssh登陆</strong>，参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/115414740\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a></p>\n<p>首先修改<code>core-site.xml</code>文件<br>\n<strong>先进入hadoop目录</strong>！！！<br>\n输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> etc/hadoop</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo vi core<span class=\"literal\">-site</span>.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在<code>configuration</code>标签内加上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;name&gt;fs.defaultFS&lt;/name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;value&gt;hdfs://localhost:<span class=\"number\">9000</span>&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;name&gt;hadoop.tmp.dir&lt;/name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;value&gt;/root/hadoop/tmp&lt;/value&gt;\t\t\t\t//这个地址的文件夹是你自定义的，不一定要和我一样</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/property&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402204602764.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n然后按下<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>退出</p>\n<p>再来配置<code>hdfs-site.xml</code>,输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vi hdfs<span class=\"literal\">-site</span>.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>同样在<code>configuration</code>标签内插入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;name&gt;dfs.replication&lt;/name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;value&gt;<span class=\"number\">1</span>&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;name&gt;dfs.namenode.name.dir&lt;/name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/tmp/dfs/name&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;name&gt;dfs.datanode.data.dir&lt;/name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/tmp/dfs/<span class=\"keyword\">data</span>&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/property&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402205204310.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n然后按下<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>退出</p>\n<p>配置root用户启动dfs服务，在<code>sbin</code>目录中<br>\n<code>start-dfs.sh</code>,<code>stop-dfs.sh</code>这两个文件最前面加上<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210403122037954.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">HDFS_DATANODE_USER=root</span><br><span class=\"line\">HADOOP_SECURE_DN_USER=hdfs</span><br><span class=\"line\">HDFS_NAMENODE_USER=root</span><br><span class=\"line\">HDFS_SECONDARYNAMENODE_USER=root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后按下<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>退出<br>\n<code>start-yarn.sh</code>,<code>stop-yarn.sh</code>两个文件最前面加上<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210403122134717.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">YARN_RESOURCEMANAGER_USER=root</span><br><span class=\"line\">HADOOP_SECURE_DN_USER=yarn</span><br><span class=\"line\">YARN_NODEMANAGER_USER=root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后按下<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>退出</p>\n<p>然后输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./bin/hdfs namenode <span class=\"literal\">-format</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402211921352.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402211929936.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n再输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./sbin/<span class=\"built_in\">start-dfs</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>启动服务<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402205900537.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">jps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>会出现这些进程<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402205944358.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n在浏览器中输入<code>localhost:9870</code>访问<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402210848885.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./sbin/<span class=\"built_in\">stop-dfs</span>.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>停止服务<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210402211506121.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"java实现单链表增加、删除、反转功能","link":"2023/07/28/java实现单链表增加、删除、反转功能"},"next":{"title":"git忽略已add文件的变动","link":"2023/07/28/git忽略已add文件的变动"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Hadoop伪分布式安装/","toc":[{"id":"hadoop伪分布式安装","title":"Hadoop伪分布式安装","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"608 字约 4 分钟"}